{"tid":2442022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：有「暈針」記錄47歲男子官涌打疫苗後頭暈送院","createTime":"2021-03-11T05:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T06:11:15.000Z","uid":290404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e57b43f36239f7446c97fd8c285b892b3cd564a","tid":2442022,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再有市民懷疑接種疫苗後出現不適。一名47歲男子早上近10時，在官涌體育館的新冠疫苗接種中心接種科興疫苗後，於休息區觀察期間感頭暈，由救護車送往伊利沙伯醫院。<br />\n<br />\n接種中心表示，該名男士沒有長期病患，但曾有「暈針」記錄，送院前清醒，一切維生指數正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579967-20210311.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579967-20210311.htm&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=d06b4306\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579967-20210311.htm&h=d67873bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579967-20210311.htm</a>"},{"pid":"73324e89d42b5647261bc5df317cdbc6e419f2b5","tid":2442022,"uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beeb3fb88abdde0f770b32d60616427a154f2b0f","tid":2442022,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:04:32.000Z","msg":"藍屍又可以作文係whatsapp流傳了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e5b5fa895a82b3b21d97b3daf56c740297eec7","tid":2442022,"uid":189160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"又官涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba78cc4088f5b52907223efefacef42e05f6632","tid":2442022,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99e5b5fa895a82b3b21d97b3daf56c740297eec7","tid":2442022,"uid":189160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"又官涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"所以標題唔寫咩牌子"},{"pid":"3ca611281397e4f2cdf2a6c722246162a67c67d8","tid":2442022,"uid":183090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"明知有暈針紀錄，都仲打科興，係咪想為國家添煩亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734ffcec0b919fc3f33242c3674bc6f5a787e462","tid":2442022,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:10:57.000Z","msg":"愈來愈年輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fe772193f932bfb255159eb61ef2a277fdf5e3","tid":2442022,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"依家政府叫科興疫苗做<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">克爾來福</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「克爾來福」適用於預防新型冠狀病毒（SARS-CoV-2）感染所致的2019冠狀病毒病（COVID-19）。<br />\n<br />\n此疫苗產品是根據《預防及控制疾病(使用疫苗)規例》(第599K章)獲認可使用，<span class=\"red\">它尚未根據《藥劑業及毒藥條例》(第138章)在香港註冊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n「克爾來福」適用於18歲及以上人群的預防接種。已有的臨床試驗數據顯示，60歲及以上人群接種本疫苗後會產生一定程度的中和抗體。<span class=\"red\">本疫苗於中國境外Ⅲ期臨床試驗中60歲及以上人群所佔比例較低（5.10%），60歲及以上人群保護效力證據尚不充分。</span>後續臨床試驗將繼續開展60歲及以上人群保護效力研究，進一步獲取該人群保護效力的證據。相關醫療機構使用本疫苗時，需結合60歲及以上人士的健康狀態和暴露風險，評估接種本疫苗的必要性。<br />\n<br />\n即係政府係未有足夠證明之外就鬆手俾佢通過"}],"pinned":{"pid":"73324e89d42b5647261bc5df317cdbc6e419f2b5","tid":2442022,"uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}